public boolean isUTCCalculationDisabled()
Indicates whether the UTC equivalents for Propertys of type LogicalType.DATE_AND_TIME will be calculated.

Returns:
true if the UTC equivalents for Propertys of type LogicalType.DATE_AND_TIME will not be calculated; false if they will be calculated.

setUTCCalculationDisabled

public void setUTCCalculationDisabled(boolean isUTCCalculationDisabled)
Sets whether UTC calculation is disabled.

Parameters:
isUTCCalculationDisabled - true to specify that the UTC equivalents for Propertys of type LogicalType.DATE_AND_TIME should not be calculated; false if they should be calculated.
